* D watched as Fenox came up to the training room doors, sniffing the edges 
as them as she steps into the room, looking at her and coming into the coom 
himself as she motions.
He did a little hop, skip and a jump to make sure his tail didn't get caught 
in the door, walking up beside Fenox and then sniffing the floor before 
raising his head and looking at her.*

" What do we do?"

* He meant, what were they going to do. Fight bots, creatures, be in a 
dangerouse situation. What?
Basically, D had faught it all.
Rolling his shoulders to stretch the muscles, he waited to see what was 
going to happen.*
